channel.title: Java not recognized as a internal
channel.description:
Java not recognized as an internal or an external program. I've got it, and I don't know why. Can somebody please help me? I can play the webclients but when I play any downloaded client it keeps giving me this error.
Please help. I tried searching and found nothing.
